statement.title: Problem Description
statement.content:
Here is a function f(x):
　　　int f ( int x ) {
　　　    if ( x == 0 ) return 0;
　　　    return f ( x / 10 ) + x % 10;
　　　}

　　　Now, you want to know, in a given interval [A, B] (1 <= A <= B <= 109), how many integer x that mod f(x) equal to 0.

statement.title: Input
statement.content:
The first line has an integer T (1 <= T <= 50), indicate the number of test cases.
　　　Each test case has two integers A, B.

statement.title: Output
statement.content: For each test case, output only one line containing the case number and an integer indicated the number of x.
